1.28.22  9:48 pm   what song are you talking about in money/got some money when you said "Hello, it's a Tuesday show
'Cause Wednesday seems so long ago
I said it three or four songs ago"? I tried to find it but I'm not sure...

      i was just using songs as a way to measure time. i'm expressing the sentiment of "it's time for the show", and i often tend to imagine that i wish i could have a new piece of material ready for release each tuesday. This has been a goal that i've been fantasizing about for a long time. when i say "i said it 3 or 4 songs ago", really what i mean is i say it all the damn time
